NK132(no)005:1: // gsang chen sngags kyi smon lam rdo rje'i rgya mdud
NK132(no)005:2: kyi rnam par bshad pa zab gsang bdud rtsi'i rol
NK132(no)005:3: mtsho zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK132(no)005:4: na mo rat+na m+au la tra y+aa ya /
NK132(no)005:5: gang gi chos nyid sgrib bral mkha' dbyings su //
NK132(no)005:6: lhan skyes sku bzhi'i snang ba 'bum brdal ba'i //
NK132(no)005:7: dkon mchog rtsa gsum rgya mtsho'i thugs rje'i zer //
NK132(no)005:8: dad brgya'i ge sar bzhad pas cir yang len //
NK132(no)005:9: mi 'gyur mchog gi 'od gsal bde ba'i dngos //
NK132(no)005:10: 'pho med zung 'jug rdo rje'i phyag rgya ru //
NK132(no)005:11: yongs shar gsang 'dzin dpa' bo gter chen rje'i //
NK132(no)005:12: zhabs la dngos po kun gyi phyag gis btud //
NK132(no)005:13: 'khor 'das shes bya kun gyi chos can dang //
NK132(no)005:14: chos nyid rjes zhugs blo gros mi zad pa'i //
NK132(no)005:15: 'jigsa brala smra ba'i seng ge chos kyi mdzod //
NK132(no)005:16: 'khor lo'i dbang phyug gdod ma'i mgon pos skyong //
NK132(no)005:17: mchog gi zhal lung dri med bdud rtsi'i char //
NK132(no)005:18: snying dbus dad pa'i rol mtshor sim pa las //
NK132(no)005:19: zab don gsang ba'i sgra ldan legs bshad rlabs //
NK132(no)005:20: rab dkar zla ba'i phreng bzhin 'di na spel //
NK132(no)005:21: zhes khyad par gyi dgos pa dang 'brel ba'i phyir
NK132(no)005:22: mchod brjod dang dam baca'i tshig gis mtshams sbyar te
NK132(no)005:23: / gang bshad par bya ba'i chos ni gsang chen bla na med pa'i smon lam /
NK132(no)005:24: rdo rje'i tshig gi rgya mdud can zhes bya ba
NK132(no)005:25: chos rgyal gter bdag gling pas mdzad pa 'di nyid
NK132(no)005:26: yin la / de ji ltar 'chad pa la gsum /
NK132(no)005:27: bsngo ba'i dpang po gsol ba /
NK132(no)005:28: bsngo rgyu'i dge rtsa bstan pa /
NK132(no)005:29: bsngo ba dngos kyi tshul lo //
NK132(no)005:31: bla ma yi dam lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK132(no)005:33: gu ru'i sgra las drangs na /
NK132(no)005:34: bla ma zhes pa lung rtogs yon tan gyi khur lci zhing /
NK132(no)005:35: skyabs gnas ji snyed pa'i spyi gzugs sam /
NK132(no)005:36: ngo bo nyid kyi na bla na ma mchis pa'i don te /
NK132(no)005:39: de kho na nyid man ngag ston pa'i sgo nas
NK132(no)005:40: rang rgyud smin grol du byed pa'i bka' drin gang
NK132(no)005:41: las thob pa de ni rtsa ba'i bla ma yin
NK132(no)005:42: la / de dang ngo bo dbyer med pa dgongs
NK132(no)005:43: rig rna bar brgyud pa'i sku gsum rig 'dzin gyi
NK132(no)005:44: tshogs grangs med pa dang bcas pa rnams so //
NK132(no)005:46: rang gi sgo gsum dang lha'i gsang gsum dbyer med
NK132(no)005:47: du shes pa'i yid kyi lam khyer las mi 'da'
NK132(no)005:48: ba'i dam tshig gis bsgrub par bya ba'i ye shes
NK132(no)005:50: lhan skyes bde ba chen po rtogs pa'i ye shes mthar phyin pa dang /
NK132(no)005:51: rnam pa kun ldan gyi stong gzugs dkyil 'khor rab 'byams su shar ba gnyis /
NK132(no)005:52: ro gcig tu gyur pa'i zung 'jug ye shes kyi sku yin la /
NK132(no)005:53: de yang rgyud sde bzhi dang 'brel ba'i zhi khro'i lha tshogs dpag tu med par snang yang /
NK132(no)005:54: gdul bya'i mos ngor tha dad pa tsam las /
NK132(no)005:55: don du na bdag cag gi ston pa gdod ma'i
NK132(no)005:56: sangs rgyas nyid kyi ye shes sgyu ma'i snang brnyan
NK132(no)005:58: gzhan yang yi dam gyi lha dang spyod yul mthun
NK132(no)005:59: par 'jug nus pa'i ye shes la ches dbang ba
NK132(no)005:60: gnas gsum gyi dpa' bo dang rnal 'byor ma dam
NK132(no)005:61: can chos skyong dang bcas pa ste /
NK132(no)005:62: de lta bu'i rtsa ba gsum gyi lha tshogsa rnams /
NK132(no)005:63: rang bzhin chos kyi dbyings las rnam 'gyur gzugs sku'i rol mo mkha' khyab tu sad de /
NK132(no)005:64: dge rtsa rdzogs byang du bsngo ba'i bden dpang dang /
NK132(no)005:65: smon lam 'grub pa'i mthun 'gyur gyi slad du /
NK132(no)005:66: thugs brtse ba chen pos gzigs shing dgongs su gsol zhes mkhyen pa gsol ba'o //
NK132(no)005:67: gnyis pa bsngo rgyu'i dge rtsa bstan pa ni //
NK132(no)005:68: deng 'dir brtson pas bsgrubs pa'i dge ba dang //
NK132(no)005:69: dus gsum bsags dang yod pa'i dge ba rnams //
NK132(no)005:70: bsdom ste zhes pas bstan te /
NK132(no)005:71: deng 'dir tshom bu tshogs sgrub sogs yul dge ba
NK132(no)005:72: la spro ba'i sems kyis drangs te sgo gsum chig
NK132(no)005:73: dril du brtson pas bsgrubs pa'i dge ba 'di dang
NK132(no)005:76: 'gro kun dge ba ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK132(no)005:77: byas dang byed 'gyur de bzhin byed pa gang //
NK132(no)005:78: zhes gsungs pa ltar rang gzhan skye 'gro yongs kyis
NK132(no)005:79: dus gsum du byas pa'i bsagsa pa'i dge ba dang
NK132(no)005:80: / rang bzhin gyis yod pa'i dge tshogs chos nyid
NK132(no)005:81: bde gshegs snying po'i khams dge ba dang bcas pa
NK132(no)005:82: rnams blos gcig tu bsdom ste bsngo ba yin la
NK132(no)005:84: dwags brgyud pa kha cig gi 'dod pa 'gog pa'i slad du /
NK132(no)005:85: yod pa'i dge ba sems nyid bde gshegs snying po zhes /
NK132(no)005:86: chos nyid la mtshan mar bzung nas bsngo bar 'dod
NK132(no)005:87: pa 'di grangs can gyis shes rig gi skyes bur
NK132(no)005:88: sgro btags pa'i log rtog dang mtshungs par bkod nas
NK132(no)005:90: gsor mi rung ba'i lta ngan gyi tshang tshing lhag
NK132(no)005:91: med du sreg pa la dus matha'i zhugs chen dang
NK132(no)005:92: 'dra ba'i lung rigs tshad mar nges te /
NK132(no)005:93: phyogs snga mar gnad thog tu me btsar song ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)005:95: 'od srung gang zag tu lta ba ri rab tsam bskyed pa ni sla'i /
NK132(no)005:96: stong pa nyid la lta ba ni de ltar ma yin no //
NK132(no)005:99: rgyal ba rnams kyis stong pa nyid //
NK132(no)005:100: lta kun nges par 'byin par gsungs //
NK132(no)005:101: gang dag stong pa nyid lta ba //
NK132(no)005:102: de dag bsgrub tu med par gsungs //
NK132(no)005:103: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK132(no)005:105: spyi tsam du chos nyid la rang bzhin gyis yod pa zhes pa dang /
NK132(no)005:106: de nyid dge ba yin par bshad pa dang /
NK132(no)005:107: de la bsngo ba'i brda' sbyor tsam 'god pa la ni 'gal bar mi bsam ste /
NK132(no)005:110: thog ma med dus can gyi dbyings //
NK132(no)005:111: sems can kun gyi gnas yin te //
NK132(no)005:116: gang zhig kun tu ma shes na //
NK132(no)005:117: srid pa gsum du rnam 'khor ba //
NK132(no)005:118: sems can kun la nges gnas pa'i //
NK132(no)005:122: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste //
NK132(no)005:123: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK132(no)005:124: zhes chos nyid bde gshegs snying po la rang bzhin
NK132(no)005:125: 'gyur ba med pa tsam gyi ngos nas yod pa'i
NK132(no)005:126: sgras bsnyad pa mang du 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK132(no)005:127: de nyid dge bar bshad pa'ang /
NK132(no)005:131: don dam pa'i dge ba gsum las /
NK132(no)005:132: phyi ma 'di de bzhin nyid la bshad pas /
NK132(no)005:133: de dang chos dbyings bde gshegs snying po gcig par ma zad /
NK132(no)005:134: rgyan stug po bkod pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK132(no)005:135: kun gzhi rang lugs dge ba ni //
NK132(no)005:136: rgyal sras rnams kyis mthong thos te //
NK132(no)005:137: kun gzhi mchog tu dge ba ni //
NK132(no)005:140: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal te //
NK132(no)005:141: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po dge //
NK132(no)005:142: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)005:143: 'o na sems tsam pa ltar kun gzhi'i rnam shes
NK132(no)005:144: la bde gshegs snying po bden grub 'dod pa dang
NK132(no)005:147: bden grub 'dod pa grub matha'i blo skyon yin gyi /
NK132(no)005:148: 'dir stong gsal 'gag med kun khyab kyi rang bzhin
NK132(no)005:149: mtha' dang bral ba'i chos nyid la bder gshegs snying
NK132(no)005:151: de nyid la bsngo ba'i tha snyad kyang gsungs te /
NK132(no)005:153: nyi ma'i 'od zer phog pa na //
NK132(no)005:154: de dag so so'i yon tan 'byin //
NK132(no)005:155: de bzhin kun gzhi'i rnam shes 'di //
NK132(no)005:156: bde gshegs snying po'i khams dge ba //
NK132(no)005:159: de ji ltar bsngo ba'i tshul ni /
NK132(no)005:160: chos nyid sems kyi gnas lugs rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i dge ba nyid /
NK132(no)005:161: glo bur gyi dri ma las grol te rang gnas
NK132(no)005:162: chos sku'i yon tan mngon du gsal bar 'dod pa'i
NK132(no)005:163: sgo nas / khams byang chub tu 'gyur bar smon pa'am bsngo ba yin la /
NK132(no)005:164: tshul de ltar byas na gzhi 'bras dbyer med kyi don la'ang nges shes drangs pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)005:165: 'di sngon du btang nas dge rtsa gzhan thams cad
NK132(no)005:166: kyang gzhi 'bras mtshams sbyor gyi rgyu kho nar bsngo
NK132(no)005:167: shes pa byung tshe theg chen sngags lugs kyi bsngo
NK132(no)005:169: don dam pa ni chos nyid tsam du ma zad
NK132(no)005:170: dge rtsa gzhan la'ang mtshan 'dzin ma spangs na bsngo
NK132(no)005:172: spangs na bsngo ba mtshan nyid pa yin pa'i tshul /
NK132(no)005:174: gal te mtshan mar byed na byang chub bsngo ma yin //
NK132(no)005:175: ci ste mtshan ma med na byang chub bsngo ba yin //
NK132(no)005:177: 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i shes rab khyad par can dang nam yang 'bral mi rung la /
NK132(no)005:178: des na dug med kyi bsngo ba ji lta ba
NK132(no)005:179: bzhin 'phags pa'i sa ma gtogs med kyang so skye'i
NK132(no)005:180: sar / rgyal ba sras bcas kyis ji ltar bsngosa pa'i rjes su slob cing /
NK132(no)005:181: de bzhin du bsngosa na 'khor gsum yang dag gi bsngo ba rjes mthun par 'gyur la /
NK132(no)005:182: des bsngo ba mtshan nyid pa'i go yang chod par gsungs te /
NK132(no)005:183: dper na tshong mi shes pas rang gi nor rdzas
NK132(no)005:184: tshong pa mkhas pa gzhan la bcol na de dang
NK132(no)005:185: khyad med pa'i khe skyed thob pa bzhin no snyam
NK132(no)005:186: du dgongs so // spyi don gsum pa bsngo ba dngos la /
NK132(no)005:187: rang don 'bras bu dang lam gyi ched du bsngo ba dang /
NK132(no)005:188: gzhan don bstan pa dang 'gro ba'i don du bsngo ba gnyis /
NK132(no)005:190: mthar thug 'bras bu'i ched du bsngo ba dang /
NK132(no)005:191: gnas skabs lam gyi ched du bsngo ba gnyis las /
NK132(no)005:193: bla med byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK132(no)005:195: ched du bya ba gzhan don du /
NK132(no)005:196: byang chub gsum gyi nang nas bla na med pa'i
NK132(no)005:197: byang chub mi gnas pa'i myang 'das chen po rdzogs
NK132(no)005:198: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob pa'i rgyur bsngo
NK132(no)005:199: ba ste / gzhan don du dge rtsa rdzogs byang
NK132(no)005:200: du stob pa theg chen bsngo ba'i mtshan nyid yin
NK132(no)005:201: ba ste / pa'i phyir ro // de yang /
NK132(no)005:202: thob bya sangs rgyas la spangs rtogs kyi yon tan
NK132(no)005:203: khyad par can mnga' ba la dmigs nas de nyid
NK132(no)005:204: thob pa'i ched du bsngo ba ma yin gyi /
NK132(no)005:205: ci ste na byang sems kyi don du nyer bya ni gzhan don 'ba' zhig yin pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)005:207: gzhan don phun tshogs sangs rgyas kyi //
NK132(no)005:208: 'bras bu gtso bo yin par brjod //
NK132(no)005:210: sangs rgyas la ni nam mkha' ji srid bar gzhan
NK132(no)005:211: don nyams pa med pa'i phrin las phun sum tshogs
NK132(no)005:212: pa yod cing / bdag gis kyang de thob na
NK132(no)005:213: de 'dra bar 'gyur ro snyam du rtag khyab lhun
NK132(no)005:214: grub kyi phrin las kho na'i rgyur bsngo dgos te
NK132(no)005:215: pa yod cing / / bzang po spyod pa las /
NK132(no)005:216: nam mkha'i mthar thug gyur pa ji tsam par //
NK132(no)005:217: sems can ma lus mtha' yang de bzhin te //
NK132(no)005:218: ji tsam las dang nyon mongs mthar gyur pa //
NK132(no)005:219: bdag gi smon lam mtha' yang de tsam mo //
NK132(no)005:221: gnyis pa lam gyi ched du bsngo ba la /
NK132(no)005:222: lam gyi rten phun sum tshogs par bsngo ba dang /
NK132(no)005:223: lam dngos nyams su len par bsngo ba /
NK132(no)005:224: lam gyi byed las 'grub par bsngo ba /
NK132(no)005:225: lam gyi mthun rkyen tshang bar bsngo ba dang bzhi las /
NK132(no)005:226: dang po lam gyi rten ni /
NK132(no)005:227: deng nas byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK132(no)005:228: rigs bzang blo gsal nga rgyal med pa dang //
NK132(no)005:229: snying rje che zhing bla ma la gus ldan //
NK132(no)005:230: dpal ldan rdo rje'i theg la nges gnas shog /
NK132(no)005:232: deng gi skye srid 'di nas brtsams te /
NK132(no)005:233: phyi'i byang chub snying po rdo rje'i gdan gyi shing drung du mchis shing /
NK132(no)005:234: nang ltar na sems nyid bde gshegs snying po'i khams
NK132(no)005:235: sgrib bral du gyur te mngon par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK132(no)005:236: chub kyi bar de srid du /
NK132(no)005:237: spyir mtho ris kyi yon tan bdun gyis mdzes pa'i dal 'byor gyi rten dang /
NK132(no)005:238: khyad par de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs theg chen gsang
NK132(no)005:239: sngags kyi lam la thog ma nyid nas 'jug sgo'i
NK132(no)005:240: rten 'brel 'grigs pa'i skal bzang can du skye ba
NK132(no)005:241: dang / skyes thob kyi shes rab dang /
NK132(no)005:242: sbyor byung gi blo gros mchog tu gsal bas shes
NK132(no)005:243: bya bden gnyis kyi tshul la thogs med du 'jug
NK132(no)005:244: nus shing / rang gi yon tan la rloms pa dang /
NK132(no)005:245: pha rol khyad du gsod pa'i nga rgyal med cing dag snang ngang gis che ba dang /
NK132(no)005:246: chos kyi rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems snying rje chen po'i rigs sad cing rgyas pa dang /
NK132(no)005:247: mtshan nyid kun ldan gyi bla ma la rgyu mtshan
NK132(no)005:248: shes nas dad pa thob pa'i mos gus 'gyur med
NK132(no)005:249: dang ldan pa / ji ltar khas blangs pa'i spang
NK132(no)005:250: blang dam tshig gi gnas la srog ltar gces pa
NK132(no)005:251: dang ldan pa / ste / don 'di dag dpal bde mchog gi rgyud las /
NK132(no)005:252: rigs su skyes dad dam tshig can //
NK132(no)005:253: skyo med kye yii rdo rje ston //
NK132(no)005:254: bla ma la gus snying rjer ldan //
NK132(no)005:255: skye shing skye bar 'gyur bar shog /
NK132(no)005:257: lag pas rdo rje dril bu 'khrol //
NK132(no)005:258: zab mo'i chos ni klog pa dang //
NK132(no)005:259: btsun mo'i shu kra mnyam zas can //
NK132(no)005:260: skye zhing skye bar 'gyur bar shog /
NK132(no)005:262: rten khyad par can de lta bu la brten nas /
NK132(no)005:263: rgyal kun bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam yon tan thams
NK132(no)005:264: cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa'i dpal dang ldan
NK132(no)005:265: pa / gzhi lta ba bden gnyis dbyer med kyi don /
NK132(no)005:266: lam sgom pa bskyed rdzogs dbyer med du bsgoms pas /
NK132(no)005:267: 'bras bu mthar phyin sku bzhi dbyer med kyi go
NK132(no)005:268: 'phang la bde myur du 'degs pas na rdo rje'i
NK132(no)005:269: theg pa ste / zab mo'i lam de la the
NK132(no)005:270: tshom bral ba'i ngesa shes thob nas tshul bzhin du
NK132(no)005:271: spyod cing gnas par shog cig pa'o //
NK132(no)005:272: de yang dge rtsa 'dis de dang de lta bur
NK132(no)005:273: gyur cig ces bsngo smon gzhi mthun du bya ba'i
NK132(no)005:274: don tshig mtha' gzhan kun la'ang dran dgos so //
NK132(no)005:275: gnyis pa lam dngos nyams su len par bsngo ba la /
NK132(no)005:276: lam spyi'i ched du bsngo ba dang /
NK132(no)005:277: lam bye brag gi ched du smon pa gnyis las /
NK132(no)005:279: dbang gis smin cing dam tshig sdom par ldan //
NK132(no)005:280: rim gnyis lam la bsnyen sgrub mthar phyin nas //
NK132(no)005:281: dka' ba med par rig 'dzin go 'phang bgrod //
NK132(no)005:282: dngos grub rnam gnyis bde blag 'grub gyur cig /
NK132(no)005:284: gsang sngags la 'jug pa'i sgo ni dbang gisa phyed dgos shing /
NK132(no)005:286: gsang sngags rang nyid kyis len pa'i nyes dmigs thob pa dang /
NK132(no)005:287: lam la 'bad pa don med du 'gyur ba'i phyir thog mar kho nar dbang len dgos /
NK132(no)005:289: gdod nas grub pa'i rtsa rlung thig le dri bcas ye shes kyi khams te /
NK132(no)005:290: 'bras bu sku bzhi'i sa bon nam /
NK132(no)005:291: bsgrub gzhi rang la gnas pa ni nyer len gyi rgyu dang /
NK132(no)005:293: rang gnas kyi ye shes sad par byed pa'i lhan
NK132(no)005:294: cig byed rkyen ni thog ma'i smin byed nyiid yin
NK132(no)005:295: la / de yang rgyu rten gyi dkyil 'khor so so la brten nas /
NK132(no)005:296: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang dbyer med pa'i bla
NK132(no)005:297: ma sku bzhi'i bdag nyid can las dbang bzhi rdzogs
NK132(no)005:298: par len cing rgyud smin nges su bsgrub dgos /
NK132(no)005:299: smin pa'i tshad kyang rab dus der dbang don gyi ye shes sgra ji bzhin pa skye ba ste /
NK132(no)005:300: snang srid dag mnyam du shar ba'i lhar snang /
NK132(no)005:301: las rlung d+hu tir thim pa'i gsal stong /
NK132(no)005:302: khams kyi zhu bdes drangs pa'i bde stong /
NK132(no)005:303: nyams kyi sbubs las grol ba'i 'od gsal rnams rim pa ltar mngon du gyur nas grol ba dang /
NK132(no)005:304: de ltar min kyang dbang don gyi ye shes de
NK132(no)005:305: dang de rgyud la skye nges kyi nus pa thob
NK132(no)005:306: cing rgyur 'gyur ba'i khyad par yang dbang gis smin
NK132(no)005:309: rno la ngar btags ji bzhin du //
NK132(no)005:310: nus pa skyes pa thob pa'i tshad //
NK132(no)005:312: de ltar dbang thob nas dbang dus su khas blangs
NK132(no)005:313: pa'i dam tshig dang sdom pa la gnas dgos shing
NK132(no)005:314: / de dang mi ldan na rgyud chud zos su 'gyur ba dang /
NK132(no)005:315: ldan na lam sgrub pa don yod du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)005:317: sngags 'chang rnams don yod par bya ba'i phyir dam tshig chen po 'di ched du brjod do //
NK132(no)005:319: des gang bsrung bya'i dam tshig kyang spyi dang khyad
NK132(no)005:320: par lhag pas bsdus pa'i rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK132(no)005:321: gi rigs su gnas pa rnams te /
NK132(no)005:322: de las mi 'da' ba'i cha nas dam tshig dang /
NK132(no)005:323: dam bcas zin pa'i cha nas sdom pa'ang yin pas
NK132(no)005:324: na sngags sdom dang dam tshig ldog pas dbye ba
NK132(no)005:325: tsam las ngo bo gcig go //
NK132(no)005:326: ji ltar srung tshul yang thabs shes khyad par can gyis 'og ma'i mtshan rtog 'gog nus na /
NK132(no)005:327: so byang gi sdom pa'ang sngags kyi dam sdom du
NK132(no)005:328: gnas 'gyur zin pas de nyid ltar bsrung ba dang
NK132(no)005:329: / gal te gnas 'gyur ma thub na dgag dgos
NK132(no)005:330: kyi gnad brtsis te sdom gsum 'gal med du srung
NK132(no)005:331: ba'i sgo nas dam tshig dang sdom pa rgyud la
NK132(no)005:333: de nas bskyed rdzogs rim pa gnyis kyi lam dngos
NK132(no)005:334: la bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi ldan gyis 'jug ste
NK132(no)005:337: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi lam gnyis las /
NK132(no)005:339: stong pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin las /
NK132(no)005:340: kun snang snying rje'i 'phen pas gtso bor bskyed rim
NK132(no)005:341: lha'i gsal snang la rtse gcig pa'i bsam gtan kho
NK132(no)005:342: nas tshogs sbyor gyi lam bgrod cing /
NK132(no)005:343: bogs 'don tshogs sgrub kyi spyod pa las rgya dang ye rgya la brten pa'i khyad par gyis /
NK132(no)005:344: 'dod gzugs kyi lha dang skal ba mnyam pa'i rig
NK132(no)005:345: 'dzin grub nas rten der rdzogs rim lam gyis zag
NK132(no)005:346: med la sbyor ba yin la /
NK132(no)005:348: sbyor ba cho ga'i yan lag rnams rdzogs nas de bzhin nyid sgom pa yan bsnyen pa /
NK132(no)005:349: snying rje sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin la goms pa nye bsnyen /
NK132(no)005:350: phyag rgya gcig spros la brtan pa thob nas tshogs lam gyi yon tan rdzogs pa ni sgrub pa /
NK132(no)005:351: bskyed rim gyad du gyur te sbyor lam du spyod
NK132(no)005:352: pas bogs dbyung ba'ii sgrub chen dang bzhi'i rim pas
NK132(no)005:353: rang lam gyi 'bras bu thun mong gi rig 'dzin
NK132(no)005:354: la sbyor ba'o // gnyis pa bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi lam ni thabs lam dang /
NK132(no)005:356: de yang gsang sngags bla med kyi lam thams cad
NK132(no)005:357: dbang bzhi'i lam gyi ngo bo gyur pa'i bskyed rdzogs
NK132(no)005:358: gnyis sam / thabs grol gnyis kyis ma bsdus pa med cing /
NK132(no)005:359: spyir thabs shes dang bral ba'i lam gyis srid pa
NK132(no)005:360: las mi grol bas thabs grol tsam zhig ni nyan
NK132(no)005:361: thos theg pa nas mthar thug a ti yo ga'i
NK132(no)005:362: bar kun la yod dgos kyang /
NK132(no)005:363: 'dir ni thabs grol khyad par can gyi dbang du byas nas bzhag go //
NK132(no)005:364: de la grol lam gyi ngo bo'am mtshan gzhi dngos
NK132(no)005:365: ni lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med kyi lta ba
NK132(no)005:366: yul med rang gsal du mthong ba nyid dang /
NK132(no)005:367: de'i rgyu thos bsam gyi shes rab dang grogs ting nge 'dzin dang bcas pa yin la /
NK132(no)005:368: thabs lam gyi mtshan gzhi dngos ni /
NK132(no)005:369: lta ba de rtogs byed kyi thabs khyad par can /
NK132(no)005:370: rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun pa'i dbang gong ma gsang sher gyi lam dang /
NK132(no)005:371: de'i grogs tha mal snang zhen 'gog pa'i bskyed rim /
NK132(no)005:372: zhi mtha' gnon byed kyi snying rje chen po dang bcas pa rnams yin no //
NK132(no)005:373: de gnyis kyang gang rung re res ni 'bras bu
NK132(no)005:374: la sbyor mi nus pas zung du 'jug dgos na'ang
NK132(no)005:375: / rten gyi gang zag dbang po rnon po'i 'jug yul gtso bor grol lam dang /
NK132(no)005:376: rtul po'i 'jug yul thabs lam gtso che ba la dgongs te so sor gsungs so //
NK132(no)005:377: de la dang po grol lam la'ang /
NK132(no)005:380: dang po la dbang dus su rtogs grol chig chod du song ba cig char ba'i cig char dang /
NK132(no)005:381: gtan tshigs la brten nas rtogs goms chig chod du skyes pa cig char ba'i rim gyis pa ste /
NK132(no)005:382: de gnyis kyang rtogs pa skye myur bul tsam las
NK132(no)005:383: lta ba rtogs pa dang rtogs grol dus mnyam du
NK132(no)005:384: gyur / bskyed rdzogs chig chod du song /
NK132(no)005:385: dbang bzhi'i lam cig char du bgrod /
NK132(no)005:386: bsnyen sgrub bzhi dus gcig tu rdzogs nas 'phags lam
NK132(no)005:387: zung 'jug gi ngo bor son pa la khyad par
NK132(no)005:388: med do // rim gyis pa la'ang /
NK132(no)005:389: thabs dang gdams ngag la brten nas lta ba mngon sum rang ngo 'phrod kyang /
NK132(no)005:390: gnyen po rkyen thub tu ma skyes pas yengs 'khrul du shor ba dag gis yang yang bsgoms pas /
NK132(no)005:391: tshegs chung ngu'i dpe'i ye shes skyed nus pa ni rim gyis pa'i cig char dang /
NK132(no)005:392: ngo sprad kyang re zhig mngon sum rtogs pa'i skal
NK132(no)005:393: pa med pa dag sngon du bsags sbyong la 'bad
NK132(no)005:394: cing / yun ring du bsgoms pas tshegs chen pos
NK132(no)005:395: lta don la sbyor dgos pa ni rim gyis pa'i
NK132(no)005:397: de gnyis kyang rtogs dka' sla tsam las /
NK132(no)005:398: lta thog tu phyin phan chad lam bgrod tshul gcig yin no //
NK132(no)005:399: 'o na rim gyis pa'i lam bgrod tshul ji ltar zhe na /
NK132(no)005:400: lta ba stong chen de bzhin nyid la nyin par gyi nyams len dang /
NK132(no)005:401: mtshan mo gnyid kyi 'od gsal sbrel ba'i mnyam bzhag la rgyun bsrings te goms pas /
NK132(no)005:402: rlung sems dbu mar 'dus pa'i stong gzugs kyi rtags
NK132(no)005:403: snang rdzogs nas dpe'i ye shes sgra ji bzhin pa
NK132(no)005:405: kun snang snying rje'i 'phen pa las bskyed rdzogs zung
NK132(no)005:406: 'jug snang stong chu zla lta bu'i phyag rgya gcig
NK132(no)005:407: spros kyi lha'i 'khor lor ldang ba dang /
NK132(no)005:408: de nyid slar yang 'od gsal du bsdus nas rlung
NK132(no)005:409: sems tsam las grub pa'i sgyu lus kyi lha skur
NK132(no)005:410: bzhengs shing tshogs sgrub kyi spyod pas bogs byung ste
NK132(no)005:412: de yang lta ba stong chen rtogs pa yan bsnyen pa /
NK132(no)005:413: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med du shar ba nye bsnyen /
NK132(no)005:414: de nyid kyi rang gdangs bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi lha skur ldang ba sgrub pa /
NK132(no)005:415: tshogs sgrub kyi nye rgyu la brten pa sgrub chen te yan lag bzhi'i rim pas mthar phyin to //
NK132(no)005:416: lam 'di la nges rdzogs khyad par can dang /
NK132(no)005:417: sngar bshad pa'i bskyed rim rkyang pa'i lam der nges rdzogs tsam po zer /
NK132(no)005:418: nges rdzogs mthar phyin pa'i gang zag gis bshad ma
NK132(no)005:419: thag pa'i lam yang rdzogs cig char du skyed pa
NK132(no)005:420: la mos sgom khyad par can dang /
NK132(no)005:421: mos pa lam byed tsam gyi sgo nas bshar sgom
NK132(no)005:422: byed pa la mos sgom tsam po bar grags shing
NK132(no)005:423: / de gnyis la slob tshul gyi sgo nas smin
NK132(no)005:424: slob dang mos slob zhes kyang bshad de zhar la
NK132(no)005:425: / 'phros pa'o // gnyis pa thabs lam ni /
NK132(no)005:426: spyir gsang sngags bla med kyi gdul bya yin par
NK132(no)005:427: 'dra yang grol lam pa ltar thabs dang gdams ngag
NK132(no)005:428: gis ngo sprad kyang don spyi tsam las mngon sum
NK132(no)005:429: rtogs mi nus pa'i dbang po rtul po rnams kyis
NK132(no)005:430: ni ji tsam bsgom kyang tshe 'dir dpe'i ye shes
NK132(no)005:432: de dag gis dbang bzhi'i lam rim can du bgrod
NK132(no)005:433: pa'i thabs lam la gtso bor brten dgos shing de
NK132(no)005:435: bsam gtan gsum gyi man ngag dang ldan pas sbyong
NK132(no)005:436: gzhi sbyong byed tshang ba'i bskyed rim phyag rgya spros
NK132(no)005:437: bcas man chad la brtan pa thob nas /
NK132(no)005:438: skabs der gsang dbang gi lam steng sgo la gcig tu brtson pas /
NK132(no)005:439: rtsa rlung sems gsum gnad du song nas dbu ma'i
NK132(no)005:440: dbyings su srog thur 'dres pa las stong bzhis drangs
NK132(no)005:442: de las sgyu ma lta bu'i lha skur ldang ba na bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu gyur /
NK132(no)005:443: de nas dbang gsum pa'i lam gyis bogs dbyung nas
NK132(no)005:444: bzhi pa'i don gyi 'od gsal la sbyor ba ni
NK132(no)005:445: thabs lam rim gyis pa ste /
NK132(no)005:447: rten bskyed rim bstan pa yan bsnyen pa /
NK132(no)005:448: 'khrul 'khor dang bcas pa'i rlung sbyor la 'dris pa nye bsnyen /
NK132(no)005:449: dpyid thig 'bar 'dzag gi lam las snang gsum gyi ye shes skyed pa sgrub pa /
NK132(no)005:450: gsang ba'i spyod pas bogs dbyung ba sgrub chen te bzhi'i sgo nas zag med la sbyor ro //
NK132(no)005:451: yang bskyed rim dang rtsa rlung la nges pa thob pa'i gang zag gis /
NK132(no)005:452: gtso bor 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag la brten nas /
NK132(no)005:453: dga' bzhi lugs 'byung gi mthar dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes dang /
NK132(no)005:454: lugs ldog gi mthar bde ba'i nyams zhen dang bral
NK132(no)005:455: ba'i rang bzhin lhan skyes kyi ye shes bskyed nas
NK132(no)005:456: / bogs 'don gzhan la ltos mi dgos par de
NK132(no)005:457: nyid du zag med la sbyong ba ni thabs lam
NK132(no)005:460: dbang snga ma gnyis kyi lam dang /
NK132(no)005:461: phyag rgya btsal nas rgyud sbyong ba sogs bsnyen pa /
NK132(no)005:462: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul te 'du shes gsum ldan gyiis snyoms par 'jug pa nye bsnyen /
NK132(no)005:463: de las yas 'bab kyi dga' bzhi bskyed pa sgrub pa /
NK132(no)005:464: mas brtan gyi dga' bzhi bskyed pa sgrub chen te yan lag bzhi'i tshul gyis mchog 'grub bo //
NK132(no)005:465: 'di dag kyang rtsa rgyud sgyu d+r+wa las /
NK132(no)005:466: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK132(no)005:467: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen pos //
NK132(no)005:468: zhes gsungs pa'i don yin la /
NK132(no)005:469: spyir thabs grol gyi lam bgrod tshul 'di rnal 'byor
NK132(no)005:470: lnga dang bsnyen sgrub bzhi gang gi chings ltar bshad
NK132(no)005:471: kyang 'dra zhing / bsnyen sgrub bzhi po 'di yang /
NK132(no)005:472: nang gses su de ting sgom tshul lta bu re re la'ang bzhi bzhir dbye ba dang /
NK132(no)005:473: gzhan yang cho ga thun gcig dang /
NK132(no)005:475: sbyor lam tshogs sgrub man chad dang /
NK132(no)005:476: tshogs lam nas mthar lam gyi bar dang /
NK132(no)005:477: thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo dang sbyar ba sogs mang bas /
NK132(no)005:478: des na gsang sngags nang par gtogs pa'i lam gang
NK132(no)005:479: dang gang bsgom pa kun la sbyor du rung ba'i
NK132(no)005:480: phyir gang ltar bshad kyang mi 'gal bar ma zad
NK132(no)005:482: slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa'i dgongs pa'ang yin no //
NK132(no)005:483: de ltar rim pa gnyis kyi lam la bsnyen sgrub
NK132(no)005:484: yan lag bzhis bgrod pa mthar phyin par byas nas
NK132(no)005:485: / lam gyur gyi 'bras bu la sbyor tshul yang /
NK132(no)005:486: spyir gsang sngags dang mtshan nyid gnyis po'i lam myur
NK132(no)005:487: bul gyi khyad par 'di gtso bor mos spyod kyi
NK132(no)005:488: sa nas 'byed dgos pa yin gyi 'phags lam thob
NK132(no)005:489: nas theg chen yin phyin chad 'dra ba lta bur
NK132(no)005:490: gsungs pa'i phyir / des na dus kyang bskal pa grangs med la mi ltos par /
NK132(no)005:491: zla drug spogs chog dang bcas pas zag med la sbyor ba dang /
NK132(no)005:492: bya dka' ba'i brtul zhugs la mi ltos par thabs shes zab mo'i khyad par gyis /
NK132(no)005:494: 'dod yon rgyan du khyer ba'i 'jug ngogs bde ba dang /
NK132(no)005:495: theg pa bde ba la brten nas dka' ba med para gnas skabs rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK132(no)005:496: mthar thug mi slob zung 'jug gi go 'phang la mig 'phrul bzhin du bgrod pa ste /
NK132(no)005:498: kun mkhyen chen pos rgyu'i lam lnga sngags kyi rig
NK132(no)005:499: 'dzin bzhis bgrod par bzhed nas rnam smin rig 'dzin
NK132(no)005:501: de nyid dngos ni sbyor lam chos mchog chen por
NK132(no)005:502: gnas pa yin kyang lam snga ma rnams de'i rgyur
NK132(no)005:503: dgongs te de skad gsungs la /
NK132(no)005:506: lhun grub mthar lam du mdzad do //
NK132(no)005:508: nus pa thob dang ma thob pas mthong lam gnyis su phye ba ste /
NK132(no)005:509: sems nyid phyag rgya chen po'i lha skur smin kyang
NK132(no)005:510: 'byung ba'i lhag lus dwangs ma 'od gsal gyi skur
NK132(no)005:511: tshe 'dir sbyangs ma nus shing bar dor phyag rgya
NK132(no)005:512: chen du bzhengs pa rnam smin rig 'dzin /
NK132(no)005:513: lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum bcom nas
NK132(no)005:514: 'od gsal rdo rje sku 'grub cing skye 'jig med
NK132(no)005:515: par srid pa ji srid du 'gro don mdzad pa
NK132(no)005:516: lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang dang /
NK132(no)005:517: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa'i bde chen dang stong
NK132(no)005:518: gzugs kyi dkyil 'khor ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i ye
NK132(no)005:519: shes kyi sku slob pa'i zung 'jug tu bzhengs pa
NK132(no)005:521: 'dis sgom lam dgu bgrod cing nang gses su rigs lngar yang dabye'o //
NK132(no)005:522: bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor du skad cig
NK132(no)005:523: gis bzhes shing drug pa rdo rje 'chang gi rgyal
NK132(no)005:524: tshab mdzad pa rjes thob phrin las sangs rgyas dang
NK132(no)005:525: mnyam pas nam mkhas gar khyab kyi don yang ci
NK132(no)005:526: rigs sgrub nus pa ni mthar lam lhun grub rig
NK132(no)005:527: 'dzin zhes / phar phyin theg pa'i kun tu 'od dang /
NK132(no)005:528: sngags phyi pa'i rang lam gyi 'bras bu bshad pa rnams 'di dang don gcig par gsungs so //
NK132(no)005:529: de nas mthar thug nyi zla za ba'i dbang bskur mchog gi lam la brten nas /
NK132(no)005:530: shin tu phra ba'i khu rdul rlung sems kyi ngo
NK132(no)005:531: bor gnas pa ma rig bag chags kyi sa pa'i
NK132(no)005:532: yid lus kyang / 'bras bu'i mngon byang 'od gsal
NK132(no)005:533: chen por bsdus pa dang mnyam du 'pho ba'i sgrib
NK132(no)005:535: sku gsung thugs rdo rje dbyer mi phyed pa'i bde
NK132(no)005:536: ba chen po'i skur bzhengs pa ni mi slob pa'i
NK132(no)005:537: zung 'jug ste / 'di la ldog cha'i sgo nas
NK132(no)005:538: kha sbyor yan lag bdun dang 'bras chos nyer lngar
NK132(no)005:540: de ltar gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK132(no)005:541: de dag ni phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos
NK132(no)005:543: mchog sgrub pa'i zhar la thun mong gi dngos grub dbang phyug brgyad dam /
NK132(no)005:544: phra yang gi yon tan dang ldan pa'i grub pa chen po dang /
NK132(no)005:545: ral gri dang mkha' spyod sogs grub pa 'bring po dang /
NK132(no)005:546: dbang dang mngon spyod sogs grub pa chung ngu dang /
NK132(no)005:547: gzhan yang rdzas dang rig sngags la brten pa'i tshe
NK132(no)005:548: dbang grub pa sogs mang du gsungs pa rnams kyang
NK132(no)005:549: / tshogs sbyor la gnas pa'i gang zag drod thob
NK132(no)005:550: pa dag gis tshul bzhin brnyes nas gzhan don rgya
NK132(no)005:551: / cher 'byung la / de lta bu'i dngos grub
NK132(no)005:552: rnam pa gnyis po bde blag ste bde zhing myur
NK132(no)005:553: bar 'grub nas don gnyis mthar phyin par gyur cig
NK132(no)005:554: / cher 'byung la / ces smon pa'o // gnyis
NK132(no)005:555: pa lam bye brag gi ched du smon pa la'ang
NK132(no)005:557: rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i nyams len la smon pa
NK132(no)005:559: / lung na raka dong sprugs kyi nyams len la
NK132(no)005:561: / smon pa / man ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK132(no)005:562: nyams len la smon pa dang gsum /
NK132(no)005:563: dang po la'ang bzhi las snang ba sku'i dkyil 'khor la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:564: cir snang sgyur 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'khor lo rdzogs //
NK132(no)005:566: kun 'byung dang sdug bsngal bden pa thun mong gi mtshan gzhir gyur pa'i phung po lnga'am /
NK132(no)005:567: 'khor ba snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i dngos po ci dang cir snang tshad 'di rnams /
NK132(no)005:568: tha snyad du rgyu rkyen tshogs pa'i dbang gis med bzhin du sgyu ma ltar snang zhing /
NK132(no)005:569: de dag kyang phan tshun rgyu 'bras su 'brel ba ni rtog tshogs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang /
NK132(no)005:570: de ltar phung khams skye mched kyi rtog tshogs su snang ba de dag kyang /
NK132(no)005:571: snang dus nyid nas 'gog lam gyi bden pa'i rang
NK132(no)005:572: bzhin can gyi gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor ram
NK132(no)005:573: / sku dang ye shes su ye nas rnam par dag pa ni /
NK132(no)005:574: lha rtog dbyer med kyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste /
NK132(no)005:575: dbyer med yin pa'i rgyu mtshan yang /
NK132(no)005:576: snang ba 'di dag ni sems snang 'ba' zhig yin la /
NK132(no)005:577: sems kyi chos nyid ni rig stong chos sku'i ye shes yin pas /
NK132(no)005:578: de nyid kyi rang snang sku dang ye shes las 'da' mi srid cing /
NK132(no)005:579: dper na mig ser can la dung ser po snang yang /
NK132(no)005:580: snang dus nas dung gi kha dog dkar po las gzhan min pa ltar /
NK132(no)005:581: 'khrul shes kyi ngor snang ba 'di kun ma dag pa ltar snang yang /
NK132(no)005:582: snang tsam nyid nas rnam par dag pa snang srid gzhir bzhengs kyi dkyil 'khor du grub ste /
NK132(no)005:583: mthar thug rgyud dag pa'i gang zag rnams kyi gzigs ngor yang mngon sum nyid du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)005:585: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas shing //
NK132(no)005:586: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK132(no)005:587: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK132(no)005:588: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK132(no)005:589: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK132(no)005:592: dbyings stong pa nyid dang rig pa'i ye shes dbyer med pa'i chos nyid kyis /
NK132(no)005:593: chos can 'khor 'das su snang ba kun la khyab cing mnyam pa nyid du gnas pa dang /
NK132(no)005:594: dbyings rig zung 'jug gi rol par shar ba'i kun
NK132(no)005:595: rdzob tu snang ba thams cad kyang gzod ma nas
NK132(no)005:596: sku dang ye shes su dag pa ste /
NK132(no)005:597: des na chos thams cad ye nas dag mnyam bden
NK132(no)005:598: pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen po'i 'khor
NK132(no)005:599: lora lhun gyis grub cing yongs su rdzogs pa ni
NK132(no)005:600: / nges don sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yin la /
NK132(no)005:601: de lta bu'i gnas lugs mthar thug gi don de nyid /
NK132(no)005:602: blo yi spyod yul dang bral ba'i yul med rang gsal lam /
NK132(no)005:603: so so rang gi rig pas mngon sum du rtogs par gyur cig ces smon no //
NK132(no)005:604: gnyis pa sgra grags gsung gi dkyil 'khor la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:605: grags pa thams cad brjod bral sngags kyi sgra //
NK132(no)005:607: de yang sngags thams cad gang las btu ba'i gzhi
NK132(no)005:608: ma 'byung khungs ni thabs shes kyi yi ge dbyangs
NK132(no)005:609: dang gsal byed gnyis yin la /
NK132(no)005:610: 'di ltar sems can dang sems med kyi bsdus pa'i sgra skad thams cad ni /
NK132(no)005:611: dbyangs gsal gyi yi ge'i gdangs las 'phos pa'i rnam 'gyur can sha stag tu nges te /
NK132(no)005:612: tha na log 'gro khyi'i skad lta bu la brtags
NK132(no)005:613: na'ang yi ge dang h+aum sogs gsal bar rtogs pa'i
NK132(no)005:614: phyir dang / gzhan yang ngag rlung gi rang bzhin yin pa dang /
NK132(no)005:615: rlung sngags dbyer med yin pa'i gnad kyis kyang grags
NK132(no)005:616: pa thams cad rang byung gi bzlas pa yin zhing
NK132(no)005:617: / des na tha snyad du'ang sgra rang mtshan pa
NK132(no)005:618: thams cad gsung yi ger gnas pas sngags yin par
NK132(no)005:619: / grub la / gnas lugs ji bzhin pa'i dbang
NK132(no)005:620: du byas na grags pa sgra tshig tu snang ba
NK132(no)005:621: thams cad brjod bral bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos
NK132(no)005:622: nyid dbyings rig zung 'jug gi ye shes 'dus ma
NK132(no)005:623: byas pa nyid brjod pa sgra snang ltar rang shar
NK132(no)005:624: / grub la / bas na / sgra skad du
NK132(no)005:625: myong dus nas grags stong dbyer med rang rig ye
NK132(no)005:626: shes kyi rol pa las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK132(no)005:627: de lta bu'i dag mnyam dbyer med kyi gnas lugs
NK132(no)005:628: de ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i mthil
NK132(no)005:629: yin zhing / de nyid grags pa sgra gzugs su
NK132(no)005:630: snang bas na sgra nyid ye shes kyi sku yang
NK132(no)005:631: yin zhing / yin la / des na sgrar snang ngo cog chos nyid kyi rang sgra dang /
NK132(no)005:633: stong gzugs lha'i 'khor lo 'ba' zhig las gzhan min
NK132(no)005:634: pas na rdo rje sngags kyi sgra tshig bla na
NK132(no)005:636: de ltar na 'khor ba'i sgra skad la'ang /
NK132(no)005:637: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i rig sngags bzhin nus pa mi 'byung ba ci zhig snyam na /
NK132(no)005:638: sgra grags sngags su rtogs pa'i gding tshad dang ldan pa dag la ni /
NK132(no)005:639: sgra tha mal pas kyang sngags kyi nus pa mthar
NK132(no)005:640: thug pa skyed de yid skyob sngags kyi ngo bo
NK132(no)005:642: brjod pa bzang ngan gyi rjes su 'brangs nas dgag
NK132(no)005:643: sgrub chags sdang du shar ba'i yid kyi shes pa
NK132(no)005:644: nyid brjod bral gsung rdo rje'i 'khor lo skyob par
NK132(no)005:646: phal pa dag gis ni sgra la sgra rang mtshan
NK132(no)005:647: par zhen nas sngags su mi shes shing der mos
NK132(no)005:648: pa'ang mi skye bas nus pa mi 'byung la /
NK132(no)005:649: sngags dngos la ni sangs rgyas kyi gsung du 'du
NK132(no)005:650: shes shing byin rlabs 'byung du re ba'i mos gus
NK132(no)005:651: kyis 'jug pas na 'bras bu 'byung ba yin zhing
NK132(no)005:652: / des na de gnyis kyi khyad par yul can
NK132(no)005:653: blo ngos nas 'byed dgos kyi yul rang gi ngos
NK132(no)005:654: nas rdo rje'i sngags sgra yin pa la khyad par
NK132(no)005:657: grol thar lam dang 'khor ba'i sgra //
NK132(no)005:658: ji skad brjod kyang gsung mchog ste //
NK132(no)005:659: theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang //
NK132(no)005:660: log 'gro ma lus thams cad skad //
NK132(no)005:661: byang chub rdo rje gsung du bsdus //
NK132(no)005:663: de ltar 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sgra
NK132(no)005:664: skad thams cad ye nas mnyam nyid gsung rdo rje'i
NK132(no)005:665: bdag nyid yin pa ltar mngon sum du gyur cig
NK132(no)005:666: ces pa'o // gsum pa dran rtog thugs kyi dkyil 'khor la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:667: sems kyi 'gyu ba rang rig 'dus ma byas //
NK132(no)005:670: rlung gis dkrugs pa'i chu nyid rba rlabs ltar snang yang /
NK132(no)005:671: snang tsam nas chu'i mtshan nyid las gzhan ma yin pa ltar /
NK132(no)005:672: sems nyid kyi rtsal las rlung gis bskyod pa na
NK132(no)005:673: gzung 'dzin 'khrul rtog gi 'gyu ba sna tshogs su
NK132(no)005:674: shar yang shar dus nyid nas skye 'gag gnas gsum
NK132(no)005:675: dang bral ba'i rang byung gi rig pa 'od gsal
NK132(no)005:676: 'dus ma byasa pa'i chos nyid las gzhan ma yin
NK132(no)005:677: te / de'i rgyu mtshan rnam rtog gang shar gyi
NK132(no)005:678: 'gyu ba thams cad ma bcos rang sar bzhag pa
NK132(no)005:679: te / na / blo 'das chos sku'i ye shes su rjen par 'char ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)005:680: rang bzhin gzigs pa dag la myong bas grub pa'o //
NK132(no)005:681: de ltar rtog tshogs ye nas rig stong thugs kyi
NK132(no)005:682: 'khor lor gnas pa'i don ji bzhin nyid du rtogs
NK132(no)005:683: par smon pa'o // bzhi pa thams cad bde chen gyi rol par smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:684: bde chen 'du 'bral med par mngon gyur shog /
NK132(no)005:686: gzhi'i gnas lugs dbyings rig zung du 'jug pa'i ye
NK132(no)005:687: shes rang rtsal lha'i 'khor lor ma 'gags par gnas
NK132(no)005:688: pa'i dag mnyam bden pa dbyer med ni bde ba
NK132(no)005:690: gnas lugs des kun la khyab cing kun kyang de nyid kyi ngo bor ro gcig pa'am /
NK132(no)005:691: tha dad med par gnas pa ni 'du 'bral med pa'i don te /
NK132(no)005:692: des na sngar ji skad bshad pa'i snang grags rtog
NK132(no)005:693: gsum dang lha sngags ye shes kyis bsdus pa'i 'khor
NK132(no)005:694: 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam nyid bde chen gcig
NK132(no)005:695: gi rol par 'char shing de'i ngang du rdzogs pa'i
NK132(no)005:697: gang du bde chen zhes bya gcig pu nyid //
NK132(no)005:698: gcig pu'i tshul gyis du ma'i gar mdzad do //
NK132(no)005:700: de lta bu'i gzhi rgyud bden gnyis dbyer med kyi don nyid lta bas gtan la phebs shing /
NK132(no)005:701: sgom pas ngang 'khyol ba'i tshul gyis mngon du gyur
NK132(no)005:702: nas don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog cig ces
NK132(no)005:703: pa'o // don gnyis pa lung na raka dong sprugs
NK132(no)005:704: kyi nyams len la smon pa la'ang bzhi las dang
NK132(no)005:705: po sgrib pa ye dag gi bshags pa'i tshul la
NK132(no)005:706: pa'o // smon pa ni / nyams chag rtog sgrib ma spangs gnas su dag /
NK132(no)005:708: sdom pa dang dam tshig gi 'gal zlar gyur pa'i nyes ltung la zhugs pas /
NK132(no)005:709: rgyud la sngar yod kyi sdom pa'i yon tan las nyamsa shing /
NK132(no)005:710: de nyams pas phyis 'byung gi yon tan skye ba
NK132(no)005:711: dang 'phel ba'i gegs byed cing dge ba'i rgyun 'gog
NK132(no)005:713: dper na bya ba chag pa lta bu'am /
NK132(no)005:715: snod kyi chag grum ltar rgyud la nyes skyon gyi sel zhugs pas kyang de skad ces bya'o //
NK132(no)005:716: nyams chag de'i ngo bo ni /
NK132(no)005:717: 'khor gsum bden zhen gyi rtog pa dang /
NK132(no)005:718: chags sogs nyon mongs pa'i rtog pa gnyis yin te /
NK132(no)005:720: bden 'dzin gyi rnam rtog las tshul min yid byed skye la /
NK132(no)005:721: de las nyon mongs skye zhing /
NK132(no)005:722: des mi dge ba'i 'du byed la sbyor ba'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)005:723: rtog pa de gnyis ni thar pa dang rnam mkhyen la sgrib pa'i dri ma yin la /
NK132(no)005:724: de dag kyang rten 'brel gyi dbang gis glo bur du sgyu ma ltar snang tsam las /
NK132(no)005:725: don dam dpyod pa'i rigs ngor spang bya'i gzhi ma grub pas ci zhig spang /
NK132(no)005:727: ma spangs ma bsgyur ba rang sor glod pa na
NK132(no)005:728: dri ma nyid ye shes su rang gsal ba'i phyir
NK132(no)005:729: sems nyid skye med kyi gnas su dri ma gdod
NK132(no)005:730: nas yod ma myong bas rang bzhin ye dag chen
NK132(no)005:731: por gnas so // tshul de ltar rtogs na bag
NK132(no)005:732: chags kyi gzhi stong pas rnam smin las grol ba'i
NK132(no)005:733: phyir bshags pa thams cad kyi rgyal por gsungs te
NK132(no)005:734: por gnas so // / thar pa chen po las /
NK132(no)005:736: drang por 'dug la yang dag ltos //
NK132(no)005:737: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK132(no)005:741: stong nyid kyi go yul tsam la gdengs bcas nas /
NK132(no)005:742: gang ltar spyod kyang bden par ma grub pas nyes
NK132(no)005:743: pa med ces chad ltas rgyas 'debs byed pa ni
NK132(no)005:744: / tha snyad kyi bden pa nyams par byed pa 'jig rten rgyangs 'phen pa'i gsang tshig ste /
NK132(no)005:745: rang nyid legs su 'dod pa dag gis mnyan pa tsam yang spang ngo //
NK132(no)005:746: des na ji srid bdag 'dzin dbyings su ma nub pa de srid du /
NK132(no)005:747: rten byung gi dngos pos bslu bar mi srid pa'i
NK132(no)005:748: phyir stobs bzhi'i bshags pa la nan tan du bya
NK132(no)005:749: ba dang / sgrib pa ye dag gi don la
NK132(no)005:750: nges shes thon nas bden zhen dbyings su 'gog pa'i
NK132(no)005:751: nyams len la brtson pa gnyis sbrel te /
NK132(no)005:752: bden gnyis zung 'jug gi bshags pas rgyud dag par bya ba ni gnad kyi don no //
NK132(no)005:753: de ltar chags nyams rtog pa'i dri ma gshis la mi gnas pa'i don mngon du gyur nas /
NK132(no)005:754: bden 'dzin gnyis snang gi 'ching ba thams cad mnyam
NK132(no)005:755: nyid bde chen gyi klong du grol bar smon pa'o
NK132(no)005:756: // gnyis pa yon tan ye ldan gyi bskang ba'i don la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:757: phyi nang gsang ba dbyer med rtogs pas bskang //
NK132(no)005:759: phyi 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ba'i gzung yul dang /
NK132(no)005:760: nang de la mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i rtog tshogs dang /
NK132(no)005:761: gsang ba de dag gi 'dug tshul phyin ci ma log pa'i gnas lugs te /
NK132(no)005:762: de gsum yang ye nas dbyer med du gnas pa yin la /
NK132(no)005:764: dbyings ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK132(no)005:765: ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK132(no)005:766: gnyis su med pa bde chen byang chub sems kyi
NK132(no)005:767: dkyil 'khor zhes gshis lugs dkyil 'khor rnam gsum 'du
NK132(no)005:769: snang tshul la 'khor 'das shes bya'i dngos po yod rgu ltar ma 'dres pa 'char yang /
NK132(no)005:770: gnas tshul la phyi nang gi chos thams cad gsang
NK132(no)005:771: ba dbyings dang ye shes zung du 'jug pa'i byang
NK132(no)005:772: chub kyi dkyil 'khor du yongs su rdzogs shing dbyer
NK132(no)005:773: med pas na / khams gsum bde ba chen por ye grol du gnas pa ste /
NK132(no)005:775: phyogs bcu'i stong khams ye nas dben //
NK132(no)005:776: srid pa gsum ni dag pa'i zhing //
NK132(no)005:777: snyigs ma lnga ni bde ldan gnas //
NK132(no)005:778: phung po lnga ni rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK132(no)005:779: thams cad mchog gi snying po bas //
NK132(no)005:780: gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi btsal //
NK132(no)005:784: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK132(no)005:786: 'byung dang 'byung 'gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK132(no)005:787: zhes pa ltar bde ba chen po'i rtsal snang 'khor ba ltar snang dus nas /
NK132(no)005:790: gsang ba yab yum zung du 'jug pa'i lha dang
NK132(no)005:791: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du bkod pas 'khor 'das
NK132(no)005:792: dbyed med pa'o // zhes bshad pa ni /
NK132(no)005:793: ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs te /
NK132(no)005:794: snga ma dang don gnad gcig tu babs so //
NK132(no)005:795: de ltar phyi nang gsang ba dbyer med kyi don mngon sum du rtogsa pasa ni /
NK132(no)005:796: sngar gnas lugs kyi don las gol zhing mtshan 'dzin
NK132(no)005:797: gyi 'khrul bar ltung nas yon tan las nyams pa'i
NK132(no)005:799: slar yang mnyam nyid byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor
NK132(no)005:800: du sor chud cing nyams pa kha bskang bas na
NK132(no)005:801: chos nyid don gyi bskang ba zhes kyang bya la
NK132(no)005:802: / de lta bu'i don gyi nyams len la rang dbang 'byor par smon pa'o //
NK132(no)005:803: zhar byung spros bcas kyi skong ba ni /
NK132(no)005:804: phyi yo byad rdzas kyi bskang ba /
NK132(no)005:805: nang phung po rten gyi bskang ba /
NK132(no)005:806: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi bskang ba ste /
NK132(no)005:807: dong sprugs kyi skong chen gsum du grags shing /
NK132(no)005:809: sman gtor rak+ta mar me bzhi bzhir tshang ba'i skong
NK132(no)005:810: rdzas kyi dag pa dran par byas nas 'phrul dag'i
NK132(no)005:812: rang snang ye shes kyi 'khor lo dgyes pa skyed cing /
NK132(no)005:813: rgyu des tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i mthu las nyams chag
NK132(no)005:814: sor chud pa'am kha skong bar byed pa'i don no
NK132(no)005:815: // gsum pa rgyud nyon mongs rang grol gyi nyams len la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:816: gang shar rang grol kun bzang klong yangs su //
NK132(no)005:818: dge mi dge lung ma bstan gyis bsdus pa'i rtog pa gang shar yang /
NK132(no)005:819: shar dus nyid nas 'grol byed kyi gnyen po gzhan la ltos mi dgos par /
NK132(no)005:820: de nyid rig stong 'od gsal gyi 'khor lo rang grol mngon sum du 'char la /
NK132(no)005:821: de nyid kyi ngang du rtsol med rang sar bzhag pas /
NK132(no)005:822: chu'i ri mo ltar shar grol la rgyun chad med cing /
NK132(no)005:823: re dogs kyi zhen 'khris stor te lta bsgom spyod
NK132(no)005:824: 'bras chig chod du gnas pa'i sems nyid ma bcos
NK132(no)005:826: mtshan rtog gi skyon las grol zhing /
NK132(no)005:827: rang bzhin la 'gyur ba med pas kun tu bzang po ste /
NK132(no)005:829: gshis gang du'ang ma grub pa /
NK132(no)005:830: gdangs bde chen du ma 'gags pa /
NK132(no)005:831: rtsal sna tshogs su shar ba /
NK132(no)005:832: bsgom bya sgom byed thams cad las 'das pa'i gsal rig rjen ne ba /
NK132(no)005:833: spros pa dang bral ba ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin
NK132(no)005:834: du gnas pa ni don kun tu bzang po dang
NK132(no)005:835: / rjes shes skye 'gag gnas gsum gang shar gyi
NK132(no)005:836: rang ngo la bltas pas rang grol gyi ye shes
NK132(no)005:837: gsal la mi rtog pa ni nyams kun tu bzang
NK132(no)005:838: / po yin la / gnas lugs de nyid rtogs ma rtogs kyi byed pas /
NK132(no)005:839: 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i 'char gazhi'am 'byung khungs su gyur bas klong ngam /
NK132(no)005:842: klong chen po chos kyi dbyings na bzhugs pa /
NK132(no)005:844: dbyings de'i mtshan nyid ni yangsa pa zhes /
NK132(no)005:845: gzung 'dzin gang du'ang rgya ma chad cing /
NK132(no)005:846: snang stong gang du'ang phyogs su ma lhung ba'i /
NK132(no)005:847: blo bral bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas lugs phyal ba chen po ste /
NK132(no)005:848: tshul de lta bu'i dbyings su yul dang yul can
NK132(no)005:849: ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i nyams len tshad du phyin
NK132(no)005:850: nas nyon mongs rang grol du smon pa'o //
NK132(no)005:851: bzhi pa 'bras bu ngan song dong sprugs kyi tshul la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:852: ngan song dong sprugs srid zhi mnyam gyur cig /
NK132(no)005:854: de ltar rang grol chos nyid kyi klong du gnyis snang nub pa'i tshe /
NK132(no)005:855: sred len gyi 'ching ba chad pas bag chags kyi nus pa yal /
NK132(no)005:856: 'du byed kyi las rgyun 'gogs bas phyis 'byung gi
NK132(no)005:857: rnam smin stong ste sdug bsngal mngon gyur gyi sa
NK132(no)005:858: pa ngan song gsum gyis mtshon /
NK132(no)005:859: 'gro ba drug gi las snang sdug bsngal bag chags bcas pa'i rtsal snang thams cad /
NK132(no)005:860: gdod ma'i gzhi klong du thim nas 'khor ba myang
NK132(no)005:861: 'das su grol ba la dong nas sprugs zhes bya
NK132(no)005:863: dong nas sam rtsa ba rming nas phyungs shing /
NK132(no)005:864: snod sprugs rdeb tshar ba ltar rang rgyud kyis bsdus
NK132(no)005:865: pa'i sdug bsngal phra rags thams cad lhag med du
NK132(no)005:869: mya ngan 'das mtha' gang yin pa //
NK132(no)005:870: de nyid 'khor ba'i mtha' yin te //
NK132(no)005:871: de gnyis khyad par cung zad ni //
NK132(no)005:872: shin tu phra ba'ang yod ma yin //
NK132(no)005:874: ye nas srid pa 'khor ba dang /
NK132(no)005:875: zhi ba myang 'das gnyis chos nyid 'od gsal gyi klong na ro gcig pa'am /
NK132(no)005:876: 'pho 'gyur med par mnyam pa nyid yin pa la /
NK132(no)005:877: yin pa ltar mngon du gyur pa mthar thug cing /
NK132(no)005:878: de dang lhan cig tu gzhan snang gi 'khor ba
NK132(no)005:879: dong nas sprugs pa'i phrin las rtsol med du 'byung
NK132(no)005:881: mnyam nyid bde ba chen po'i ye shes de nyid
NK132(no)005:882: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje chen po'i ngo bo
NK132(no)005:885: de lta bu'i gnas la mnga' dbang rdzogs par gyur cig ces smon pa'o //
NK132(no)005:886: spyi don gsum pa man ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i nyams len la smon pa la bzhi las /
NK132(no)005:887: dang po thig le rang gnas kyi lta ba la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:888: thig le chen po sku dang zhing khams rdzogs //
NK132(no)005:890: de yang sems nyid ma bcos pa'i gnas lugs 'dus
NK132(no)005:891: ma byas pa rig stong ka dag gi lta ba
NK132(no)005:892: ni / yid dpyod mtshan 'dzin gyi spros pa'i grwa zur spangs shing /
NK132(no)005:893: chos sku'i dgongs pa mthar thug pa'am /
NK132(no)005:894: nges pa'i don gyi snying por gyur pa'i phyir thig le chen po ste /
NK132(no)005:895: de'i ngang du lhun grub 'od gsal gyi 'char gzhi
NK132(no)005:896: go ma 'gags par gting gsal gyi tshul du gnas
NK132(no)005:897: shing / de lta bu'i ka dag lhun grub zung
NK132(no)005:898: du 'jug pa'i gdod ma'i ye gzhi de nyid ngo
NK132(no)005:899: bo rang bzhin thugs rje'i bdag nyid can gyi gzhir
NK132(no)005:901: gzhi dbyings 'od gsal gyi zhing khams kyang yin la
NK132(no)005:902: des na rig stong thig le nyag gcig gi klong
NK132(no)005:903: du dbyings nang gsal gyi sku dang zhing khams thams
NK132(no)005:904: cad rang bzhin babs las grub pas na gzhon nu
NK132(no)005:905: bum sku'i dkyil 'khor zhes kyang bya'o //
NK132(no)005:906: de'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK132(no)005:907: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin rlung lnga'i gdangs g.yos pas lhun grub kyi phyi rgya ral te /
NK132(no)005:908: dag pa myang 'das kyi sgo ka dag stong pa'i
NK132(no)005:909: dbyings su mya ngan las 'das pa'i sku dang zhing
NK132(no)005:910: snang thams cad rang byung du bkod cing /
NK132(no)005:911: ma dag 'khor ba'i sgo dmigs pa med pa'i snying
NK132(no)005:912: rje'i rang gdangs 'gro ba drug gi gdul zhing 'dul
NK132(no)005:913: byed dang bcas pa'ang rang snang du 'char bas /
NK132(no)005:914: thugs rje phyir gsal gyi sku dang zhing khams thams
NK132(no)005:915: cad kyang rig pa'i thig ler rdzogs pa yin la
NK132(no)005:916: / tshul de ltar nges par byas nas /
NK132(no)005:917: gzhi rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba rang gnas kyi
NK132(no)005:918: don de nyid mngon sum 'od gsal gyi tshul du
NK132(no)005:920: gnyis pa bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:921: dam tshig chen po spang blang mtshan ma dag /
NK132(no)005:924: de bas dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK132(no)005:925: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK132(no)005:927: gzhi sems kyi gnas lugs rig stong mtha' bral du rtogs pa'i gshis der /
NK132(no)005:929: gnyis su 'dzin pa'i spros pa gang yang ma grub pas /
NK132(no)005:931: yon tan las nyams pa'ang mi srid cing /
NK132(no)005:932: de lta bu'i don las mi 'da' ba ni dam tshig chen po yin te /
NK132(no)005:933: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul dngos la zhugs shing
NK132(no)005:934: 'dus ma byas kyi tshul khrims dang zag med kyi
NK132(no)005:935: sdom pa mthar thug pa la gnas pa'i phyir ro
NK132(no)005:936: // de'i tshe kun nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK132(no)005:937: rnam par byang ba'i phyogs kyi chos thams cad brjod bral gyi rig pa nyag gcig tu rtogs nas /
NK132(no)005:940: dgag sgrub sogs gnyis chos kyi mtshan ma thams cad gnyis med lta ba'i klong du dag cing /
NK132(no)005:941: sdom pa gsum gyi bcas mtshams ji snyed pa'ang der 'dus shing rnam par dag go //
NK132(no)005:942: 'di la ldog chas dbye na bzhi ste /
NK132(no)005:943: sems nyid ka dag gi klong na spang gnyen gang
NK132(no)005:944: yang ma grub par rtogs nas bsrung mtshams kyi mtshan
NK132(no)005:945: 'dzin med pa lta ba'i don dang /
NK132(no)005:946: rgya mtsho las gza' skar ltar /
NK132(no)005:947: gzugs yul la der 'dzin med cing sgo lnga rang
NK132(no)005:948: yan phyal ba gu yangs su gnas pa sgom pa'i
NK132(no)005:949: don te / gtso bo ka dag gi dam tshig gnyis dang /
NK132(no)005:951: 'khor 'das su snang ba thams cad sems nyid gcig pa'i rang bzhin du rtogs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK132(no)005:952: spros med ka dag gi klong du 'gags med lhun
NK132(no)005:953: grub kyi 'char sgo lhag med du rdzogs par rtogs
NK132(no)005:954: nas snang ba bzhi'i nyams len dang mi 'bral ba
NK132(no)005:955: sgom pa ste / gtso bo lhun grub kyi dam tshig gnyis bstan to //
NK132(no)005:958: bsrung mtshams med pa med pa'i dam tshig dang //
NK132(no)005:959: gzung dang 'dzin pa med pas phyal pa yin //
NK132(no)005:960: thams cad sems su 'dus pas gcig pu nyid //
NK132(no)005:961: lhag ma med par rdzogs pas lhun gyis grub //
NK132(no)005:963: de ltar bsrung du med pa ye bsrung chen po'i
NK132(no)005:964: dam tshig gi don rtogs nas spangs blang mtshan 'dzin
NK132(no)005:965: gyi dri ma thams cad rig stong zang thal gyi
NK132(no)005:966: dbyings su dag par smon pa'o //
NK132(no)005:967: gsum pa 'du 'bral med pa'i nyams len la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:968: khyab brdal chen po re dogs mdud pa grol //
NK132(no)005:970: de ltar lta ba klong du gyur cing rig pa yul med du song ba'i tshe /
NK132(no)005:971: blta bya lta byed dang bcas pa'i bzung dran gyi 'ching ba dbyings su chad de /
NK132(no)005:972: rtsal snang chos can du snang ba kun la /
NK132(no)005:973: rang snang ris med du rtogs pa'i chos nyid kyis khyab cing /
NK132(no)005:974: gang snang gang shar thams cad rig stong chos sku'i yo langs su brdal ba ni /
NK132(no)005:975: dper na nam mkha'i dbyings ltar gtad med rgya yan /
NK132(no)005:977: mngon sum 'od gsal chen po'i 'khor yug tu gyur nas /
NK132(no)005:978: rang bzhag chu bo rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas shing /
NK132(no)005:982: gnyen po la mchog tu 'dzin pa dang /
NK132(no)005:983: spang bya la skyon du lta ba sogs /
NK132(no)005:984: re dogsa gnyis 'dzin gyi mdud pa thams cad brjod bral mnyam nyid kyi klong du grol nas /
NK132(no)005:985: gyi ling sgrog las thar ba ltar phyogs bral gu yangs su gyur /
NK132(no)005:986: yengs yul chos nyid du dag /
NK132(no)005:987: dran med 'od gsal la gnas pa ste /
NK132(no)005:989: dran snang rang grol chos nyid ngang //
NK132(no)005:990: khyab brdal nam mkha'i 'khor yug la //
NK132(no)005:991: dran pas gzung dang ma gzung med //
NK132(no)005:992: dran pas sgrog bcings mthol lo bshags //
NK132(no)005:995: tshul de lta bu'i 'du 'bral med pa'i nyams len
NK132(no)005:996: gyi sgom pa sgra ji bzhin pa la rang byan
NK132(no)005:998: bzhi pa spang thob med pa'i 'bras bu la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:999: rdzogs pa chen po chos sku mngon gyur shog /
NK132(no)005:1001: da ltar gyi sems nyid ma bcos pa 'di nyid
NK132(no)005:1002: dri mas gshis la ma gos pas skyon ye dag
NK132(no)005:1003: / ye shes rang byung du gsal bas yon tan
NK132(no)005:1004: ye rdzogs te spang thob med pa'i 'bras bu rang
NK132(no)005:1006: 'di las gud na sangs rgyas gzhan med pas gzhi 'bras dbyer med yin la /
NK132(no)005:1007: de'i don tshul bzhin rtogs pa na /
NK132(no)005:1008: theg pa 'og ma ltar rim rtsol la ltos mi dgos par rtsol bral rang babs /
NK132(no)005:1009: byar med blo 'das kyi ngang du sa lam chig chod du rdzogs /
NK132(no)005:1010: rlung sems gzhi dbyings su thim nas /
NK132(no)005:1011: da lta nyid du ye shes bla ma'i sa la gnas pa mthar phyin cing /
NK132(no)005:1012: de'i klong na lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan thams cad rdzogs pa dang /
NK132(no)005:1013: thob bya mthar thug tu gyur pas na 'bras bu rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya ste /
NK132(no)005:1014: de ni spangs rtogs kyi chos tshad med pa'i ngo bo'am /
NK132(no)005:1015: rten gzhir gyur pa'i phyir chos kyi sku'i bdag nyid do //
NK132(no)005:1016: 'di la ldog chas dbye na dbyings nang gsal gyi sku gsum zhes /
NK132(no)005:1017: rang bzhin ye dag la glo bur 'phral dag gis
NK132(no)005:1018: khyad par du byas pa'i dbyings 'gyur ba med pa'i
NK132(no)005:1019: cha ni mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku dang phra ba'i
NK132(no)005:1020: ye shes thim lam rmugs pa mkhyen cha 'gag med
NK132(no)005:1021: du gsal ba'i cha nas zhi ba chos sku dang
NK132(no)005:1022: / dbyings rig 'du 'bral med pa'i ye shes de
NK132(no)005:1023: nyid stobs sogs yon tan rgya mtsho'i ngo bor bzhugs
NK132(no)005:1024: pa'i cha nas mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ste
NK132(no)005:1026: de lta bu'i chos sku de nyid ji ltar mngon du gyur pa'i tshul ni /
NK132(no)005:1028: shes rab chen po skad cig la //
NK132(no)005:1029: chos kun khong du chud pa 'chang //
NK132(no)005:1031: gzhi snang gi dngos po rang ngor snang tsam nas /
NK132(no)005:1032: rig pa nyag gcig tu bye brag phyed cing /
NK132(no)005:1033: phyed thog der chos kyi skur grol nas /
NK132(no)005:1034: spyi gzhi las grol gzhir 'phags te /
NK132(no)005:1035: gzhan las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu /
NK132(no)005:1036: thog ma'i gzhi thog tu rang sar gnas pa ste
NK132(no)005:1037: kun tu bzang po'i khyad chos drug gi sgo nas
NK132(no)005:1038: skad cig gis grol ba'i ka dag chen por sangs
NK132(no)005:1039: rgyas shing / de'i tshe dmigs med thugs rje'i 'jug
NK132(no)005:1040: pa phyir gsal du shar te sku gsung thugs rnam
NK132(no)005:1041: pa thams cad pa'i ngo bo gyur pa'i phrin las
NK132(no)005:1043: nam mkha' ji srid du srid zhi'i gdung ba sel
NK132(no)005:1044: ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa rtsol med du
NK132(no)005:1045: 'byung ngo // de ltar lhun grub rang gnas kyi
NK132(no)005:1046: 'bras bu spang thob bral ba'i don la myur du
NK132(no)005:1047: reg par shog cig ces pa'o //
NK132(no)005:1048: man ngag rdzogs chen ltar smon pa'i sho lo ka 'dis ni /
NK132(no)005:1049: rkang pa dang pos ka dag lhun grub zung 'jug
NK132(no)005:1050: gi lta ba bstan pas gzhi rdzogs pa chen po
NK132(no)005:1051: dang / bar pa gnyis kyis rang grol gyi spyod pa dang /
NK132(no)005:1052: rang bzhag gi sgom pa gnyis ka thun mong du bstan pas lam rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK132(no)005:1053: rkang pa tha mas bsal bzhag dang bral ba'i chos
NK132(no)005:1054: sku bstan pas 'bras bu rdzogs pa chen po ste
NK132(no)005:1055: / theg mchog 'od gsal snying po'i brjod don thams cad lhag med du bsdus so //
NK132(no)005:1056: de yan gyis lam dngos la smon pa song nas /
NK132(no)005:1057: spyi don gsum pa lam gyi byed las 'grub par bsngo ba ni /
NK132(no)005:1058: brgyud pa gsum gyi byin rlabs snying la zhugs //
NK132(no)005:1059: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam gsang sems la rdzogs //
NK132(no)005:1060: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub pa yis //
NK132(no)005:1061: mu mtha' med pa'i 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK132(no)005:1063: de yang rang snang gi 'og min na /
NK132(no)005:1064: ston 'khor thams cad ye shes 'od gsal ba'i ngang
NK132(no)005:1065: du dgongs klong ro gcig par bzhugs pa ni rgyal
NK132(no)005:1068: theg pa thams cad kyi 'phro gazhi'am brjod byar gyur
NK132(no)005:1069: pas na brgyud pa kun gyi 'byung khungs yin la
NK132(no)005:1070: / de nas gzhan snang longs sku'i ston pas rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung ngam /
NK132(no)005:1071: sku'i brda thabs la brten nas /
NK132(no)005:1072: 'phags pa'i sar bzhugs pa'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi rgyud
NK132(no)005:1073: la rgyal ba'i dgongs pa rim gyis skyed pa ni
NK132(no)005:1075: de rnams kyis lha klu mi'i gdul bya so so la rjod byed rgyud sde dang /
NK132(no)005:1076: brjod bya smin grol gyi gdams pa stsal ba zhal
NK132(no)005:1077: nas snyan dang thugs nas thugs su brgyud cing deng
NK132(no)005:1078: sang bar du 'ong ba la gang zag snyan brgyud
NK132(no)005:1079: ces grags shing / yang snga ma gnyis gcig tu
NK132(no)005:1080: bgrangs pa la rgyal ba dgongs brda'i brgyud pa dang
NK132(no)005:1081: ces grags shing / / de nas 'khor tshom bu
NK132(no)005:1082: dang bcas pa zag med rig 'dzin gyi sar gshegs
NK132(no)005:1083: pa ji snyed cig byung ba la rig 'dzin rig
NK132(no)005:1085: 'khor dang bcas te gshegs mi nus pa'i mtshams man
NK132(no)005:1086: chad la rnal 'byor rna bar brgyud pa zhes bzhed
NK132(no)005:1087: de / bshad rgyud rgya mtsho las /
NK132(no)005:1088: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor ba //
NK132(no)005:1089: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK132(no)005:1091: de ltar 'chad tshul gnyis po de yang dbye bsdu'i
NK132(no)005:1092: khyad par tsam las don gnad gcig pa'i phyir gang
NK132(no)005:1094: de lta bu'i brgyud pa de dag gi thugs rje dang ye shes ma lus pa ni /
NK132(no)005:1095: rtsa ba'i bla ma la rdzogs te /
NK132(no)005:1097: sems nyid ye sangs rgyas pa'i don mngon du byas
NK132(no)005:1098: nas rgyal ba kun dang thugs yid 'dres pas dgongs
NK132(no)005:1099: brgyud rdzogs shing / dgongs pa de yang mos gus kyi nyer len dang /
NK132(no)005:1100: brgyud pa gong ma'i byin rlabs kyi brda thabs la
NK132(no)005:1101: brten nas thugs rgyud du 'phos pas brda brgyud rdzogs
NK132(no)005:1102: pa dang / sngon nas da lta'i bar du zam
NK132(no)005:1103: ma chad par byung ba'i rgyud lung man ngag gi
NK132(no)005:1104: gdams pa thams cad mnga' bas snyan brgyud kyang rdzogs
NK132(no)005:1105: pa dang / pa'i phyir / des na bla ma ni /
NK132(no)005:1108: sangs rgyas dngos byon yin par ma zad /
NK132(no)005:1109: rang ngor bka' drin sangs rgyas las kyang lhag par
NK132(no)005:1110: shes pa'i mos gus kyis thugs yid dbyer med du
NK132(no)005:1111: bsre ba'i bla ma'i rnal 'byor nyid lam gyi srog
NK132(no)005:1112: tu bzung nas / bskyed rdzogs kyi lam gang sgom
NK132(no)005:1113: yang bsgrub bya bla ma'i ye shes kyi sku dang
NK132(no)005:1114: tu bzung nas / / 'od gsal gyi thugs 'ba'
NK132(no)005:1115: zhig rang rgyud du sgrub pa yin par shes dgos
NK132(no)005:1116: tu bzung nas / / shing / mdor na nyams
NK132(no)005:1117: len kun la des khyab par byed pa ni gnad
NK132(no)005:1119: de dang bral ba la dngos grub mi 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK132(no)005:1121: gang phyir rdo rje 'dzin pa yis //
NK132(no)005:1122: dngos grub slob dpon rjes 'brang gsungs //
NK132(no)005:1124: de ltar bla ma'i mos gus bsgoms pa'i byed las sam /
NK132(no)005:1126: brgyud pa gsum gyi byin rlabs thams cad wa kha
NK132(no)005:1127: nas chu 'dren pa ltar bla ma'i thugs rje la
NK132(no)005:1128: brten nas rang gi snying la cig char du zhugs
NK132(no)005:1129: shing don brgyud kyi dgongs pa lon /
NK132(no)005:1131: don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa sogs 'byung ba'o //
NK132(no)005:1132: de nas gzhi lta ba dag mnyam bden pa dbyer med kyi don gtan la phab nas /
NK132(no)005:1133: lam sgom pa bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi ting nge
NK132(no)005:1134: 'dzin nyams su blang ba ni bla na med pa'i
NK132(no)005:1135: lam yin la / de yang phung khams skye mched
NK132(no)005:1136: kyi rtog tshogs sgyu ma ltar snang ba nyid lha
NK132(no)005:1137: dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin du 'phrul cing /
NK132(no)005:1138: de gnyis ye nas ngo bo bdag gcig tu 'brel
NK132(no)005:1139: bas na lhar rtog dbyer med kyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK132(no)005:1140: ba ste / de'i don gzhung bzhin bsgom pa ni zab gsal gnyis med kyi bskyed rim dang /
NK132(no)005:1141: stong nyid sgyu ma'i rang gdangs rig pa ye shes
NK132(no)005:1142: su 'phrul pa'i dbyer med bde ba chen po ni
NK132(no)005:1143: / nges don sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste /
NK132(no)005:1144: de'i don mtshan bcas kyi thabs la brten nas mtshan
NK132(no)005:1145: med 'od gsal la sbyor ba'i tshul du sgom pa
NK132(no)005:1147: de gnyis zung du 'jug pa la sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK132(no)005:1148: ba'i lam gsang zhes bya ste thun mong ma yin
NK132(no)005:1149: pa'i zab don dbang rab kyi 'jug ngogs yin pa'i
NK132(no)005:1150: phyir ro // lam de bsgoms pa'i byed las ni /
NK132(no)005:1151: brtson pa'i lag rjes sems la shar te rang sems
NK132(no)005:1152: ye nas zung 'jug ye shes kyi lha skur rdzogs
NK132(no)005:1153: pa'i don mngon du gyur pa yin la /
NK132(no)005:1154: de yang sbyor lam du rlung sems tsam gyi lha sku /
NK132(no)005:1155: mthong lam du ye shes 'od gsal rkyang pa'i lha sku /
NK132(no)005:1156: sgom lam du zung 'jug gi lha sku /
NK132(no)005:1157: mi slob lam du dbyer med bde chen gyi lha
NK132(no)005:1158: sku rnams rim pa bzhin mngon du gyur pa ste
NK132(no)005:1160: rang sems phyag rgya chen po nyid //
NK132(no)005:1161: bsgoms pa mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK132(no)005:1163: de ltar tshig rkang gnyis po des gtso bor rang don gyi byed las bstan cing /
NK132(no)005:1164: de lta bu'i lam gyur gyi 'bras bur dbang 'byor ba'i tshe /
NK132(no)005:1165: gnas skabs dang mthar thug kun tu gang 'dul gyi phrin las rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK132(no)005:1167: gdul ba rnam pa bzhi'i phrin las sogs rtag khyab lhun gyis grub pa yi sgo nas /
NK132(no)005:1169: grangs dus kyi mtha' la gtugs pa med pa'i 'gro ba rgyud lnga'i yid can rnams /
NK132(no)005:1170: mi gnas pa'i myang 'das su sgrol bar mdzad pa ni gtso bor gzhan don gyi byed las te /
NK132(no)005:1171: rkang pa phyi ma gnyis kyis bstan nas /
NK132(no)005:1172: de ltar lam gyi byed las don gnyis phun sum
NK132(no)005:1173: tshogs pa'i yon tan la mnga' brnyes par shog cig
NK132(no)005:1174: ces smon no // bzhi pa lam gyi mthun rkyen tshang bar smon pa ni /
NK132(no)005:1175: zhi khro sprul pa'i 'khor los lung bstan cing //
NK132(no)005:1176: mkha' 'gro rnams kyis bu bzhin skyong ba dang //
NK132(no)005:1177: chos skyong srung mas bar chad kun bsal nas //
NK132(no)005:1178: yid la smon pa mtha' dag 'grub gyur cig /
NK132(no)005:1180: de yang lung ston mkhan gyi lha rang rgyud pa zhig gzhan ga shed na med kyi /
NK132(no)005:1181: rang gi sems nyid lha dang bla ma'i ngo bor
NK132(no)005:1182: ye nas dag par shes pa'i nges shes kyi lta
NK132(no)005:1184: sgom pa goms pa'i gsal snang gyad du gyur pa'i rnam par shar te /
NK132(no)005:1185: dngos nyams rmi lam ci rigs par yi dam gyi
NK132(no)005:1186: lha zhi khro sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor losa
NK132(no)005:1188: mthar thug byang chub chen por dang /
NK132(no)005:1189: gnas skabs lam dus su legs nyes thams cad lung ston par mdzad cing /
NK132(no)005:1190: des ji skad bstan pa bzhin du nyes phyogs spang
NK132(no)005:1191: zhing legs phyogs la zhugs pas lam myur du mthar
NK132(no)005:1192: phyin pa'i rkyen du 'gyur bas na mthun rkyen yin
NK132(no)005:1193: no // 'dir gsar ma'i lugs ltar na zhi ba
NK132(no)005:1194: la longs sprul gnyis char yod pa smos ma dgos
NK132(no)005:1195: kyang khro bo ni sku gsum gyi zlas phye ba'i
NK132(no)005:1196: sprul sku kho na bzhed cing /
NK132(no)005:1197: snga 'gyur gyi rgyud sder ni khro bo la'ang gnyis kar gsungs pa /
NK132(no)005:1198: des na chos sku'i klong las gzugs skur shar ba'am sprul pa'i don yin te /
NK132(no)005:1200: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal 'dud //
NK132(no)005:1203: stong pa nyid kyi mkha' la thugs rje rig pa'i
NK132(no)005:1204: rtsal shugs kyis 'gro ba'i 'phags pa chen po rnams
NK132(no)005:1205: kyis kyang rtag tu dgongs te /
NK132(no)005:1207: dam pa'i mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK132(no)005:1208: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlob //
NK132(no)005:1210: dpal chen po'i tha tshig la gnas shing gnas yul
NK132(no)005:1211: dur khrod na spyod pa'i zhing sngags lhan skyes kyi
NK132(no)005:1212: mkha' 'gro ma gsang ba'i gnyer 'dzin rnams kyis kyang
NK132(no)005:1213: bu bzhin du skyong ba'i tshul /
NK132(no)005:1216: ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa yang //
NK132(no)005:1217: gtsug gi nor bu 'bar ba ltar //
NK132(no)005:1218: g.yo sgyu med cing gus ldan cing //
NK132(no)005:1219: sems kyi blang nas spyi bo yi //
NK132(no)005:1220: gtsug tu bzhag ste bkur bar bgyi //
NK132(no)005:1221: de yi dgos pa ci yang rung //
NK132(no)005:1222: ma lus rdzogs par bdag cag bsgrub //
NK132(no)005:1223: ces sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK132(no)005:1225: dam tshig can gyi rig sngags 'chang ba ni chos skyong dam can gyi bla rdo yin pas /
NK132(no)005:1226: pho mo ma ning gi sder gtogs pa'i rgyud gsum dregs pa'i tshul can srung ma rnams kyang /
NK132(no)005:1227: sha rul la sbrang ma bzhin ma bsgrub rang 'khor du 'dus nas /
NK132(no)005:1228: sgrub pa po'i 'byung bzhi phyi'i bar chad /
NK132(no)005:1229: rtsa rlung nang gi bar chad /
NK132(no)005:1230: gzung 'dzin gsang ba'i bar chad sogs /
NK132(no)005:1231: byang chen la bar du gcod pa'i tshogs kun phyir
NK132(no)005:1232: bsal nas mthun pa'i stong grogs bgyid pa yin la
NK132(no)005:1233: / de lta bu'i lam gyi mthun rkyen tshang ba la brten nas /
NK132(no)005:1234: rnam par byang ba'i phyogs dang mthun pa'i 'dod don
NK132(no)005:1235: yid la ji ltar re zhing smon pa mtha' dag
NK132(no)005:1236: bde myur du 'grub ste don gnyis mthar phyin par
NK132(no)005:1238: da ni rtsa ba'i spyi don gnyis pa /
NK132(no)005:1239: gzhan don bstan pa dang 'gro ba'i ched du bsngo ba ni /
NK132(no)005:1240: rgyal ba'i bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK132(no)005:1241: bstan 'dzin rnams kyi bzhed pa'i don kun 'grub //
NK132(no)005:1242: ma lus skye rgu'i 'gal rkyen kun zhi nas //
NK132(no)005:1243: phun tshogs mtha' dag yid bzhin 'byor gyur cig /
NK132(no)005:1247: ston pa'i dam chos rnam gnyis te //
NK132(no)005:1248: lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid yin //
NK132(no)005:1251: mngon rtogs bslab pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che phyogs thams cad du /
NK132(no)005:1252: sgo thams cad nas dar zhing rgyas la /
NK132(no)005:1253: yun ring du gnas pa dang /
NK132(no)005:1254: bstan pa de yang bstan 'dzin gang zag gi rgyud dang 'brel ba ste /
NK132(no)005:1256: de 'dzin byed pa smra byed dang //
NK132(no)005:1257: sgrub pa byed pa kho na'o //
NK132(no)005:1259: lung gi bstan pa thos bsam 'chad nyan gyi sgo nas 'dzin pa dang /
NK132(no)005:1260: rtogs pa'i bstan pa sgrub pa nyams len gyi sgo nas 'dzin dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK132(no)005:1261: des na bstan 'dzin dge ba'i bshes gnyen de rnams
NK132(no)005:1262: kyis kyang lhag pa'i thugs bskyed kyis kun nas bslang
NK132(no)005:1263: ste bstan pa la bya ba byed pa dang /
NK132(no)005:1264: sems can la phan bde sbyin 'dod pas mtshon /
NK132(no)005:1265: thugs la ji ltar bzhed pa'i chos mthun gyi don kun gegs med yid bzhin du 'grub pa dang /
NK132(no)005:1266: de la brten nas ma lus mi lus lus pa
NK132(no)005:1267: med pa'i skye rgu yongs kyi mi 'dod pa'i dngos
NK132(no)005:1268: po / mngon mtho nges legs kyi 'byor pas phongs shing /
NK132(no)005:1269: 'khrul snang srid pa'i sdug bsngal brnag par dka' ba'i tshogs dang /
NK132(no)005:1270: de'i rgyu chos dang gang zag gi bden 'dzin dang /
NK132(no)005:1271: des bskyed pa'i las nyon gyi 'du byed mtshams sbyor dang bcas pa'i 'gal rkyen kun zhi nas /
NK132(no)005:1272: mthun phyogs su gyur pa rang rang gi dbang po'i rim pa ltar /
NK132(no)005:1273: gnas skabs su theg pa gsum la zhugs pa'i lam gyi rten dang /
NK132(no)005:1275: lam gyi 'bras bu la spyod cing /
NK132(no)005:1276: mthar thug kyang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa kho nar
NK132(no)005:1277: brten nas bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi go
NK132(no)005:1278: 'phang / spangs rtogs kyi yon tan zad mi shes pa'i dpal la dbang bsgyur ba sogs /
NK132(no)005:1279: 'phral dang yun gyi phun sum tshogs pa'i legs tshogs
NK132(no)005:1280: mtha' dag yid la ji ltar 'dod cing smon pa
NK132(no)005:1281: bzhin du 'bad rtsol med par rgyud la 'byor bar
NK132(no)005:1282: gyur cig ces smon pa dang /
NK132(no)005:1283: dge tshogs 'di la brten nas de dang de lta
NK132(no)005:1284: bur gyur cig snyam pa ni bsngo ba'ang yin no
NK132(no)005:1285: // de ltar na gzhung dbu zhabs kyi don mtha' dag rdzogs par bkral ba re zhig grub bo //
NK132(no)005:1287: 'khor 'das chos rnams kun gyi de bzhin nyid //
NK132(no)005:1288: rnam med 'od gsal 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dbyings //
NK132(no)005:1289: rnam bcas spro bsdu'i byed por yongs bzhengs pa'i //
NK132(no)005:1290: ye shes sgyu ma gsang 'dzin rdo rje chos /
NK132(no)005:1292: 1 / gang dang mi gnyis rab 'byams rgyal kun gyi //
NK132(no)005:1293: gsang ba bsam mi khyab pa'i ngo mtshar la //
NK132(no)005:1294: dbang bsgyur grub pa mchog gi zhal lung 'di //
NK132(no)005:1295: dgongs pa'i rtsal chen bdun gyi rgya yis btab /
NK132(no)005:1297: 2 / rgyud lung man ngag rgya mtsho'i rdo rje'i gnas //
NK132(no)005:1298: nyung ngu'i tshig gi sgrom du stsal ba na //
NK132(no)005:1299: zab barlinga phyag rgya'i mdud pa 'grol bzod pa'i //
NK132(no)005:1300: rnam dpyod de yang rdo rje'i sor mo bzhin /
NK132(no)005:1302: 3 / de phyir 'di don ji bzhin ston nus pa //
NK132(no)005:1303: zab gsal myur ba'i blo gros nam mkha'i ltor //
NK132(no)005:1304: shes bya kun gyi tshig don rab bskyil ba'i //
NK132(no)005:1305: 'jigsa bral slob dpon chos kyi dbang po tsam /
NK132(no)005:1307: 4 / yongs 'dzin mchog de'i gsung gsang man+d+h+aa ras //
NK132(no)005:1308: yid kyi chu mtsho yang yang bsrubs byas kyang //
NK132(no)005:1309: snying po'i gdams bcud ma lon skal dman bdag /'di 'dra'i tshig don smra la ji ltar dbang /
NK132(no)005:1311: 5 / blo gsal don gnyer rnam 'gyur dbyug gu'i lces //
NK132(no)005:1312: bskul ba'i rkyen gyis pho tshod 'ur sgra cher //
NK132(no)005:1313: bsgrags kyang rna ba gtser ba'i tsher ma las //
NK132(no)005:1314: dgos don khog pa stong pa'i rnga gog bzhin /
NK132(no)005:1316: 6 / de lta na yang spyi don rdo rje'i tshig /
NK132(no)005:1317: rtsa bar bzung nas dri med gsung gi rgyun //
NK132(no)005:1318: rang blor cung zad nges dang rtsal bshad kyis //
NK132(no)005:1319: mi 'gal don dang bstun te bsdebs par byas /
NK132(no)005:1321: 7 / ma rtogs log par rtog dang the tshom dris //
NK132(no)005:1322: dgongs pa'i don bzang bsnubs dang gsang sgrogs su //
NK132(no)005:1323: gyur pa'i nyes tshogs chos kyi spyan ldan dang //
NK132(no)005:1324: chos bdag mig yangs tshogs kun bzod mdzod cig 8 /
NK132(no)005:1325: lad mor dga' ba byis pa'i rtse 'jo bzhin //
NK132(no)005:1326: rtsom pa'i gzugs brnyan mkhas pa'i rjes phyogs te //
NK132(no)005:1327: chos dang mthun pa'i kha g.yar 'bod pa tsam //
NK132(no)005:1328: 'di las dge tshogs thob snyam cher mi bsam /
NK132(no)005:1329: 9 /'on kyang rang gi blo gros goms pa dang //
NK132(no)005:1330: skal mnyam gzhan la'ang phan pa cung zad slad //
NK132(no)005:1331: bsam pa dge bas bkod pa'i legs byas kyis //
NK132(no)005:1332: 'gro kun sku bzhi'i rgyal thabs brnyes gyur cig 10 /
NK132(no)005:1333: ces pa 'adi'ang sngon dus su mkhan chen rdo rje
NK132(no)005:1334: 'chang pad+ma badz+ra gyi zhal snga nas khyod kyis 'di
NK132(no)005:1335: la rnam bshad blos gang dpogs shig bris zhes lan
NK132(no)005:1336: mang du gsungs pa yid la bcag kyang /
NK132(no)005:1337: re zhig sgyid lug gi ngang du lus shing nye
NK132(no)005:1338: char sprul pa'i sku mchog 'jigs med kun dga' dang
NK132(no)005:1339: / sems dpa' chen po 'od zer rdo rje zung nas bka' nan gyis bskul bas mtshams sbyar te /
NK132(no)005:1340: rang nyid goms pa skye ba dang /
NK132(no)005:1341: blo gros gsar bu dag la'ang phan pa'ii blos /
NK132(no)005:1342: rmongs btsun 'du shes gsum pa kun dga' rgyal mtshan du 'bod pas yang yang dpyad de sbyar ba /
NK132(no)005:1343: 'dis kyang bstan pa'i snying po yun ring du gnas pa dang /
NK132(no)005:1344: mkha' khyab skye rgu thams cad zung 'jug bla na
NK132(no)005:1345: med pa'i go 'phang la myur du reg pa'i rgyur
